equal to outgoing flow at each of the 3 nodes. To setup our incidence
matrix, imagine that flow leaving is negative and flow incoming is
positive. The system is then:

$\begin{bmatrix}
-1 & 1 &0 \\ 
0& -1 & 1\\ 
1& 0 & -1
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}
x_{1}
\\ x_{2}
\\x_{3}
\end{bmatrix}
